    <dcterms:title>Thank You Note for Apples</dcterms:title>
    <dcterms:description>A brief thank you note dated December 2, 97, presumably 1897. The letter reads:

Dear Maud,
Papa is delighted with the apples, and ever-ever so much obliged.
Sincerely,
May-Day Harris
-The apples are lovely</dcterms:description>
